						               													<description>Description from the designer:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Fight to rule the kingdom!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;True King is a strategy game designed to either work as a team with other players or lead the kingdom all on your own.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Move your units to steal the rival kingdom&amp;rsquo;s flag and bring it back to your kingdom unharmed. Travel perilous terrain arranged by the Kings of each kingdom.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Use strategy and teamwork to topple your opponent and become the one True King.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Be a fearless King, a courageous Princess, a valiant Knight, a powerful Wizard, or a cunning Archer and rule over the land.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;As king of the land, it&amp;rsquo;s time to rule with an iron fist.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Command your forces to capture the nearby kingdom&amp;rsquo;s flag, forcing their surrender.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;In this turn based strategy game us the kingdom&amp;rsquo;s King, Knight, Wizard, Princess, and Archer to move through the land to your opponent&amp;rsquo;s kingdom.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Take turns with your opponent laying out the land with magical traps and powerups.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Use special character powers like the wizard&amp;rsquo;s ability to teleport a player anywhere they wish or the knights ability to block opponent&amp;rsquo;s movement.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Play head to head against a rival or play with a group or people, each controlling one of the characters in the kingdom, taking turns moving.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;To win the game and control all the kingdoms the player&amp;rsquo;s must capture the enemy&amp;rsquo;s flag and bring it back to their own base.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Watch out for magical traps like holding spells, teleporters, and power voiding areas as you traverse the map!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Use your wits to prove you have what it takes to be the one, True King.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
